{"tid":754751,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"笑咗😂踢街場唔俾嗌","createTime":"2018-07-24T15:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T02:15:48.000Z","uid":29952,"like":9,"dislike":114,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"dd2f01a3ed435946d840d148868d28c3706fd4df","tid":754751,"uid":29952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T15:54:53.000Z","msg":"話說今日放工約左班朋友落街踢返場友誼波<br />\n點知去到見到有十隻中學雞係度<br />\n開頭咁人多有啲朋友係場出面猜下波好正常<br />\n唔小心踢咗入場都會執返<br />\n有隻中學雞竟然燥咗話唔俾踢<br />\n<br />\n之後我朋友守波果時就大嗌咗一聲<br />\n然後個隻中學雞就話唔俾叫<br />\n我朋友就答佢街場都唔俾叫 咁幾時先可以叫<br />\n世界盃都係咁叫啦<br />\n叫隊友名大聲啲唔通又唔俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後我朋友同條友都收咗聲<br />\n然後有另一隻好矮既中學雞狂衝亂撞<br />\n到我朋友key波佢就衝埋去係咁踢<br />\n我朋友當場都燥咗嗌咗嗌<br />\n踢人果個都跟住嗌<br />\n心諗你朋友又話唔俾嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知有條懶係高既中學雞過黎話係咪兇佢<br />\n<br />\n呼籲大家踢街場真係要忍下口<br />\n最好唔好講野唔好叫<br />\n嗌隊友呀嗌補位呀呢啲都唔好<br />\n一陣嚇親啲中學雞佢地搵媽媽喊就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c31b0e40a5c5cd5c54f3292c7f7ff4853bc2375","tid":754751,"uid":29952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T15:57:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76d214ecfd1314726110f58c480b60831164b66","tid":754751,"uid":810,"like":101,"dislike":2,"score":99,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T15:58:37.000Z","msg":"廢撚到<br />\n咁都要上黎開post"},{"pid":"e001cf0f7ae5b59b93db71749f61eb718cae73b1","tid":754751,"uid":18646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a76d214ecfd1314726110f58c480b60831164b66","tid":754751,"uid":810,"like":101,"dislike":2,"score":99,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T15:58:37.000Z","msg":"廢撚到<br />\n咁都要上黎開post"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T15:59:37.000Z","msg":"咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868ce3fbabc6285a796824f13ecd9df64db0b9e8","tid":754751,"uid":69